<B>__{dockside}
<A>__{the dive boat is moored at a clumsy angle next to the police boat, where hendricks has been pulling routine maintenance. the police launch is cluttered with tools and spare parts; some non essential piece of gear is stripped and laid out on the deck. hendricks is on the dive boat, kneeling next to andrews.}
<B>__{aboard the dive boat}
<A>__{andrews is shaking, bloody froth on his lips and chest. the shaken divers are huddled together, an ambulance attendant is wheeling a gurney into position. crosby and sparky are stunned.}
