<B>__{wide on the harbor}
<A>__{the amity police boat, brody, ellen and hendricks aboard, is headed under full power out to sea. hendricks is pumping the horn, warning boats out of the way, ignoring the rules of the road; as small boats scatter out of the way, we can see the ambulance, red light flashing, pushing out slowly through the crowd at dockside.}
